Package: otel-dpu
Version: SED__DPU_AGENT_PKG_VERSION
Section: base
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Depends: jq
Maintainer: Forge team <swngc-forge-dev@nvidia.com>
Description: OpenTelemetry for site controller DPUs
 This package installs the OpenTelemetry collector. It expects a JSON file at
 /etc/site-dpu.json containing "site" and "domain" values and an array of
 "endpoints" in the form { "fqdn": "some.fqdn", "ip": "10.0.0.1" } including
 carbide api and otel ingress. A post-install script reads this file and updates
 /etc/hosts and sets hostname. OTLP export uses mTLS certs under /opt/forge.
